ion of cinephiles and their use of new technologies. With the advent of home theaters, digital recording devices, online film communities, cinephiles today pursue their dedication to film outside of institutional settings. A radical new history of film culture, Cinephilia breaks new ground for students and scholars alike.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aMotion picture audiences. 0aMotion picturesxHistory. 0aMotion picturesxSocial aspects. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / General.2bisacsh1 aBehlil, Melis, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aElsaesser, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGorfinkel, Elena, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHagener, Malte, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHagener, Malte, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHediger, Vinzenz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHilderbrand, Lucas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLeary, Charles, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNg, Jenna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPol, Gerwin van der, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRobnik, Drehli, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSimons, Jan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSingkhra, Sutanya, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStrauven, Wanda, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aValck, Marijke de, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWindhausen, Federico, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 a